    - SAUCE: rfi-flush: Add speculation barrier before ori 30,30,0 flush
    - SAUCE: powerpc/asm: Allow including ppc_asm.h in asm files
    - SAUCE: Remove setup.h include file otherwise compilation complains about
      missing header file.
